Development in a Post-conflict Country</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">The&#13;&#13;
Strategy: Running the Country like a Business</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">Local Strife&#13;&#13;
from International Investment</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">Role of&#13;&#13;
Chiefs in Land Deals</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">Arrival of&#13;&#13;
African Minerals Limited to Tonkolili</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-1">II.&#13;&#13;
Displacement to Permit Mining</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">“It&#13;&#13;
Was Not Our Wish to Come Here”</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">Relocation&#13;&#13;
of Ferengbeya, Wondugu, and Foria</div>&#13;
    <div class="toc toc-2">Empty&#13;&#13;
Promises</div>&#13;
