from Graham Foyle-Twining, Global Head of Human Resources and Sustainable&#13;&#13;
Development, African Minerals Engineering Ltd. To Human Rights Watch, March 11,&#13;&#13;
2012, p. 9. Foyle-Twining told Human Rights Watch in October 2013, after he had&#13;&#13;
