        <span class="FootnoteTextChar">&#13;
          <span>Letter from African Minerals Limited,&#13;&#13;
March 11, 2013. At BCM, one of AML’s contractors, Ghanaian expatriate&#13;&#13;
workers, all senior staff, eat in the canteen. Sierra Leonean workers eat at&#13;&#13;
