          </span>&#13;
        </a>&#13;
        <span>UN Committee on Economic, Social and Cultural Rights (ESCR&#13;&#13;
Committee), General Comment No. 15, The Right to Water, E/C.12/2002/11 (2003).</span>&#13;
      </p>&#13;
    </div>&#13;
    <div id="ftn247">&#13;
      <p>&#13;
        <a href="#_ftnref247" name="_ftn247" id="_ftn247">&#13;
          <span class="MsoFootnoteReference">&#13;
