        <span>African Minerals Limited, “Corporate Presentation,”&#13;&#13;
January 2014, <span><a href="http://www.african-minerals.com/system/files/uploads/financialdocs/AMI_CorporatePresentation_Jan2014.pdf" name="" id=""><span>http://www.african-minerals.com/system/files/uploads/financialdocs/AMI_CorporatePresentation_Jan2014.pdf</span></a>&#13;&#13;
